                                         <h2 class="row-one-h2">What blogs do for online businesses..</h2>
                                         <p>Blogs enable online content to populate highly used keywords, if keyword search is applied properly, meaning your important tags hold highly searched words, it will cross paths with content with more prior engagements.. A blog is a great reason to have a landing page constructed that will lead up to a full sales funnel, once your online content adds up over time. Good informing blogs lead up to the demand for your solution, and a blog that is a part of a larger sales funnel increases site visits. In my own choice of words, this process becomes or works sort of like an automation that is driven by the clicks of your audience. I will go pass the limits of the typical online shop platform that you host your shop with by applying my knowledge of web development, as well as my own raw and uncut creativity. Most of the popular, and commonly used platforms that sale domains to businesses, offer great and stable enough architecture to get the job done, but lets be clear and take a look from the technical side of things, we know there are times you need to create more customized content to capture your traffic, and honestly, these platforms require developers to remain under the guidelines of pre-constructed frameworks that will limit those fully customizable abilities. So you have developers like me that offer services building your content from scratch, that will allow your audience to lead themselves directly to your main shop.</p>
